The problem in your program is that the promo and member discounts are the 
same because `raw.memberDiscount` is copied to both `promoDiscount` and `me
`memberDiscount` fields of `item` record, however you should subtract `item
`item.memberDiscount` from `price` instead of `discount`. So I changed this
this line:
```tundra
